Latest Builds

These are the very latest builds built by Travis. There is a build every time that a change is pushed to GitHub. For this reason, even though a build might have succeeded, there most likely will still be bugs in it. I try not to push bad code but it happens every once and a while. Only builds that have succeeded are shown below.
